    "title": "Senior Fleet Manager at Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Fleet Manager to strengthen our Patna-based team.\n\nAbout Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services:\nBolloré Logistics India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bolloré Logistics India Holdings Services!",
